404
00:15:59.230 --> 00:16:00.110
Entonces,

405
00:16:00.350 --> 00:16:02.475
Elena, hija de Júpiter,

406
00:16:02.555 --> 00:16:04.154
ordenó otra cosa.

407
00:16:04.555 --> 00:16:07.194
